-29T09:51:20.000Z","msg":"附近一對村民父子驚聞車禍即上前救人，但將其中一名男子救出後，私家車隨即着火自焚，並冒出大量濃煙，現場更傳出多次爆炸聲，其間<span style=\"color: red;\">獲救男子一度大叫長達分半鐘</span>，高呼：「救吓我哋！」「救命呀」，聲音痛苦，聞者心酸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fbca6e6d6c4a0447da79dea2cd0e9a8df0d0df6","tid":1082863,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:53:49.000Z","msg":"佢會唔會搵佢老婆報夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20170904/9b2e2b30ad1647f6a89cfaf9944fa2ef.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20170904%2F9b2e2b30ad1647f6a89cfaf9944fa2ef.jpeg&h=93e76f8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07b913346380d4804705e137db7b2a4e7b897f9f","tid":1082863,"uid":9726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:56:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"943001426ec1f1f0af41b2f20873d5d4736db6f5","tid":1082863,"uid":818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T10:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}